'''Dart trap''' is located in a [[inaccessible area]] within [[Kruk's dungeon]]. It was supposed to be a trap on the planned third route during the [[Monkey Madness II]] [[quest]]. It featured tripwires, floor spikes, dart traps, spinning blades, three doors, and three chests that would have presumably contained the unused item [[Combat scarred key]]. [[Kineer]] from the [[Catacombs of Kourend]] is located in the central room, and has unique dialogue when talked to.
